{"tid":171220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自問仲講理性既連登仔請入。","createTime":"2017-03-25T07:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T14:20:27.000Z","uid":45713,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11e03f5d0866fe6315855606cd101a2e65d404e3","tid":171220,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"我地唔可以再比蔣介石（翻生）拖累<br />\n反完中介 以受害者姿態上位就當自己判官<br />\n<br />\n宜家仲過隔離紅登改人圖 想做判官搵存在感<br />\n拖低連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/171015/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/171015/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n蔣生正負評反映一切<br />\n我希望大家一齊入去比負評佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/170487/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/170487/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n反紅登 反五毛 反垃圾林祖舜係一件事<br />\n但係呢條蔣介石玩到咁<br />\n第日高登收左皮之後 佢又唔知搞d咩出黎累連登<br />\n<br />\n希望大家講下理性 唔好見高登仔就反 見連登仔就盲撐"},{"pid":"11be0a8158eabcfedf5f2302739efec60344b9fc","tid":171220,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"自己人都唔幫？就算佢有錯點解唔可以大事化小"},{"pid":"cfb4879d5e077d3133a636b54d84458b90acbe33","tid":171220,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"等睇「又一隻」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bfecab52332fcf0dfb0d3d5212f8001ba0f0e6","tid":171220,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"開始懷疑反中介淋油事件既真實性"},{"pid":"5a22a5c95af3639fc14e71bf386d89d5ba3185ff","tid":171220,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:29:04.000Z","msg":"睇撚錯蔣介石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a21508fada6299e1382981245a5e45799bb9895","tid":171220,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己人都唔幫？就算佢有錯點解唔可以大事化小</blockquote><br />\n蓋清唔好膠啦<br />\n你係隔離post先屌完佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk